title: Paskahak
text: Paskahak () is a village in <a href="Rostam-e%20Yek%20Rural%20District">Rostam-e Yek Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Rostam%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Rostam%20County">Rostam County</a>, <a href="Fars%20Province">Fars Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 240, in 44 families.
